RACE.RACE_TEXT: TAMPA BAY DOWNS RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 83. Claiming Purse 20500. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 122 lbs. GREENPOINT hit the gate at the break, raced off the pace on the inside through the opening quarter, trailed the field from the two path around the turn and showed no kick. EL GUAPO raced in the middle of the pack on the outside up the backstretch, swung out to the four path coming around the turn and flattened out in the stretch.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: TAMPA BAY DOWNS RACE 4 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 73. Maiden Claiming Purse 20000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 122 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Claiming Price $16,000.
